title: Listen to Lykke Li on Kiki’s New Song “Birds”
text:
Listen to Lykke Li on Kiki’s New Song “Birds” She lends her vocals to the fellow Swedish singer’s new track Lykke Li Photo by Chelsea Lauren/WireImage 
Lykke Li has lent her vocals to the a capella version of a new song from Swedish singer-songwriter Kiki titled “Birds.” Listen to it below. Kiki (real name Kicki Halmos) is a member of Li’s touring band, as well as the Swedish rock band Masquer. Last fall, Li announced a new supergroup, LIV, and shared the songs “ Dream Awake ” and “ Wings of Love .” 
Kiki: Birds (A Cappella) [ft. Lykke Li] (via SoundCloud ) Artists In This Story
